Stud.IP - Mobile
================


Still in process - not ready to use!!


A plugin creates a mobile view for the Stud.IP-LMS.


Install Notes:
––––––––––––––
- for Dropbox use
	- PHP Pear HTTP:OAuth should be installed
	- PHP Pear Dropbox shoud be installed	
- you have to run the sql-files from the sql folder
- change the dropbox developerkey in models/dropCom.php and models/course.php

Just install it via the studip-root user. Important the plugin needs to be acceable from
the nobody-user.
You can reach the mobile-view at:
  yourstudipadress / plugins.php / studipmobile


ICONS
–––––
The Icons are from:
- http://www.glyphish.com/
- http://app-bits.com/free-icons.html
They should be changed or you have to put these links on each page.

